WEBVTT

00:03:59.219 --> 00:04:04.009
(Laughter)

00:04:04.033 --> 00:04:05.361
But not just conservatives.

00:04:05.385 --> 00:04:09.486
I also caught myself thinking mean things
about mushy, centrist liberals

00:04:09.510 --> 00:04:11.388
and greedy Wall Street bankers

00:04:11.412 --> 00:04:12.870
and Islamophobes

00:04:12.894 --> 00:04:14.368
and slow drivers,

00:04:14.392 --> 00:04:16.677
because I really hate slow drivers.

00:04:16.701 --> 00:04:19.220
(Laughter)

00:04:19.244 --> 00:04:22.244
And as I'd catch myself
in these moments of hypocrisy,

00:04:22.268 --> 00:04:25.967
either I was just noticing them
or they were getting worse,

00:04:25.991 --> 00:04:27.574
especially in the last few years.

00:04:28.149 --> 00:04:30.274
And as I felt more hateful --